{"tid":1977044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"東區護士 借錢唔還 買口罩唔比錢","createTime":"2020-04-17T16:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T12:39:03.000Z","uid":12994,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"96ef74d37db7aa98ea6a03e59e06e32ab66e83e1","tid":1977044,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"咪話我屈你地東區護士<br />\n用護士個名 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借錢唔還 買口罩唔比錢</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">借據 PASS 地址 相 我通通有齊</span><br />\n一日拖一日 拖足成個星期 日日都話今日找數<br />\n找足一星期都未找到條數<br />\n借住護士個名係度招搖撞騙<br />\n借錢果震咩都得 咩話唔會拎份工黎教飛<br />\n叫你還錢果震 就永遠諸多藉口<br />\n同你地連登仔講<br />\n聽到護士要幫手果D咪撚幫 隨時比佢地扮豬食老虎<br />\n幫人? 食人唔𦧲骨就有份<br />\n<br />\nTo某護士 <br />\n你而家好入比我,<br />\n我重可以唔開你名<br />\n今日還唔到 <br />\n等我貼你街招 + 去東區爆鳩你大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3b74f20f40651200dabc4fe52ee0e9a616d20d","tid":1977044,"uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"圖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ecbf06e14ad73bb29d2f2bd3d7a8e8fa47ed79","tid":1977044,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1967a979991a207668c4d113bb11cb243c991643","tid":1977044,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"男定女"},{"pid":"8b355fe12341ee70bf1fc72169931729755effaf","tid":1977044,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:09:04.000Z","msg":"借左幾多先？一千幾百就算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"0266a85b632efb2db1c59f665e2bfb8965732733","tid":1977044,"uid":32542,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"你而家好入比我,<br />\n我重可以唔開你名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"